# Snapshot: examples/03_fib

### Source: `examples/03_fib.frog`

```frog
proc dec int -- int do 1 - end
proc fib_step int int -- int int do dup rot + end
proc main -- do
    0 1 15
    while dup 0 > do
      rot rot
      dup print
      fib_step
      rot
      dec
    end
    drop drop drop
end
```

### Run

Command:

```text
py -m frog run examples/03_fib.frog
```

